      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 09:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于信心疲软，中国 11 月份信贷增长依然缓慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/china-s-credit-growth-disappoints-in-november-as-bond-sales-slow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[11月份中国信贷供应扩张缓慢，企业借贷疲弱和货币供应扩张缓慢令经济学家担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/china-s-credit-growth-disappoints-in-november-as-bond-sales-slow</guid>
